Symbol.Script_3D:
! Designer Chair 09
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m=0 THEN END
PEN gs_cont_pen
IF gs_shadow=0 THEN SHADOW OFF
IF GLOB_CONTEXT>20 and GLOB_CONTEXT<40 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m=1
unID=1
ADD a/2,b/2,0
HOTSPOT -a/2, -b/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -a/2, b/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT a/2, -b/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT a/2, b/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
MUL a/0.59, b/0.728, 1 ROTZ 90 ADD 0.038-0.728/2, -0.265, 0
hotspot 0.46+(zzyzx-0.1-0.015*COS(alfa))/TAN(alfa)-0.015*SIN(alfa), 0.075, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128: unID=unID+1 hotspot 0.46+(zzyzx-0.1-0.015*COS(alfa))/TAN(alfa)-0.015*SIN(alfa), 0.075, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3: unID=unID+1 hotspot 0.46+(zzyzx-0.1-0.015*COS(alfa))/TAN(alfa)-0.015*SIN(alfa), 0.075, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2: unID=unID+1
hotspot 0.46+(zzyzx-0.1-0.015*COS(alfa))/TAN(alfa)-0.015*SIN(alfa), 0.075+0.38, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128: unID=unID+1 hotspot 0.46+(zzyzx-0.1-0.015*COS(alfa))/TAN(alfa)-0.015*SIN(alfa), 0.075+0.38, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3: unID=unID+1 hotspot 0.46+(zzyzx-0.1-0.015*COS(alfa))/TAN(alfa)-0.015*SIN(alfa), 0.075+0.38, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2: unID=unID+1
IF gs_full_edit=1 THEN
hotspot -0.0352, 0.065, 0, unID, gs_seat_height, 1+128: unID=unID+1 hotspot -0.0352, 0.065, -1, unID, gs_seat_height, 3: unID=unID+1 hotspot -0.0352, 0.065, gs_seat_height, unID, gs_seat_height, 2: unID=unID+1
hotspot -0.0352, 0.465, 0, unID, gs_seat_height, 1+128: unID=unID+1 hotspot -0.0352, 0.465, -1, unID, gs_seat_height, 3: unID=unID+1 hotspot -0.0352, 0.465, gs_seat_height, unID, gs_seat_height, 2: unID=unID+1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m=1 THEN
MATERIAL gs_frame_mat BRICK 0.03,0.03,0.34+dt
ADDY 0.50 BRICK 0.03,0.03,0.34+dt DEL 1
ADDX 0.60 BRICK 0.03,0.03,0.47+dt DEL 1
ADDY 0.50 ADDX 0.60 BRICK 0.03,0.03,0.47+dt DEL 2
ADDX 0.43 ADDZ 0.03 BRICK 0.03,0.03,0.44+dt DEL 2
ADDY 0.50 ADDX 0.43 ADDZ 0.03 BRICK 0.03,0.03,0.44+dt DEL 3
ADDZ 0.53+dt ROTY 90 ADDY -0.01 ADDX 0.03 ADDZ 0.23 BRICK 0.03,0.08,0.46 DEL 5
ADDZ 0.53+dt ROTY 90 ADDY 0.46 ADDX 0.03 ADDZ 0.23 BRICK 0.03,0.08,0.46 DEL 5
Material gs_seat_mat alfa=ATN((gs_seat_height-0.3063+0.37)/0.17) ADD 0.46, 0, 0.1 ROTY 90-alfa ADD -0.015, 0, -0.07 CUTPOLY 4, 0, 0, 1, 0, 1, zzyzx, 0, zzyzx DEL 3
ADDZ 0.33+dt ROTY 90 ROTY 11 ADDY 0.065 ADDX 0.03 ADDZ -0.03 BRICK 0.015,0.4, 0.52+0.2 !+(gs_seat_height-0.3063)*TAN(21)*COS(11) DEL 6
CUTEND
MATERIAL gs_frame_mat ADDZ 0.1 ROTY 90 ADDY 0.03 ADDX 0.03 ADDZ -0.03 BRICK 0.03,0.03,0.69 DEL 5
ADDZ 0.1 ROTY 90 ADDY 0.47 ADDX 0.03 ADDZ -0.03 BRICK 0.03,0.03,0.69 DEL 5
Material gs_back_mat alfa=ATN((gs_seat_height-0.3063+0.37)/0.17) ADD 0.46, 0, 0.1 ROTY 90-alfa ADD -0.015, 0.075, -0.07 BRICK 0.015, 0.38, 0.07+(zzyzx-0.1-0.015*COS(alfa))/SIN(alfa) DEL 3
ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m=2 THEN
MATERIAL gs_frame_mat cprism_ frame_mat2, frame_mat2, gs_frame_mat, 5,0.34+dt, 0,0,15, 0.03,0,15, 0.03,0.03,15, 0,0.03,15, 0,0,-1
ADDY 0.50 cprism_ frame_mat2, frame_mat2, gs_frame_mat, 5,0.34+dt, 0,0,15, 0.03,0,15, 0.03,0.03,15, 0,0.03,15, 0,0,-1 DEL 1
ADDX 0.60 cprism_ frame_mat2, frame_mat2, gs_frame_mat, 5,0.47+dt, 0,0,15, 0.03,0,15, 0.03,0.03,15, 0,0.03,15, 0,0,-1 DEL 1
ADDY 0.50 ADDX 0.60 cprism_ frame_mat2, frame_mat2, gs_frame_mat, 5,0.47+dt, 0,0,15, 0.03,0,15, 0.03,0.03,15, 0,0.03,15, 0,0,-1 DEL 2
ADDX 0.43 ADDZ 0.03 cprism_ frame_mat2, frame_mat2, gs_frame_mat, 5,0.44+dt, 0,0,15, 0.03,0,15, 0.03,0.03,15, 0,0.03,15, 0,0,-1 DEL 2
ADDY 0.50 ADDX 0.43 ADDZ 0.03 cprism_ frame_mat2, frame_mat2, gs_frame_mat, 5,0.44+dt, 0,0,15, 0.03,0,15, 0.03,0.03,15, 0,0.03,15, 0,0,-1 DEL 3
ADDZ 0.30+dt ROTX -90 ADDY 0.03 ADDX 0.03 ADDZ -0.03 cprism_ frame_mat2, frame_mat2, gs_frame_mat, 5,0.59, 0,0,15, 0.03,0,15, 0.03,0.03,15, 0,0.03,15, 0,0,-1 DEL 5
ADDZ 0.1 ROTY 90 ADDY 0.03 ADDX 0.03 ADDZ -0.03 cprism_ frame_mat2, frame_mat2, gs_frame_mat, 5,0.69, 0,0,15, 0.03,0,15, 0.03,0.03,15, 0,0.03,15, 0,0,-1 DEL 5
ADDZ 0.1 ROTY 90 ADDY 0.47 ADDX 0.03 ADDZ -0.03 cprism_ frame_mat2, frame_mat2, gs_frame_mat, 5,0.69, 0,0,15, 0.03,0,15, 0.03,0.03,15, 0,0.03,15, 0,0,-1 DEL 5
ADDZ 0.13 ROTX -90 ADDY 0.03 ADDX 0.03 ADDZ -0.03 cprism_ frame_mat2, frame_mat2, gs_frame_mat, 5,0.59, 0,0,15, 0.03,0,15, 0.03,0.03,15, 0,0.03,15, 0,0,-1 DEL 5
ADDZ 0.13 ROTX -90 ADDY 0.03 ADDX 0.46 ADDZ -0.03 cprism_ frame_mat2, frame_mat2, gs_frame_mat, 5,0.59, 0,0,15, 0.03,0,15, 0.03,0.03,15, 0,0.03,15, 0,0,-1 DEL 5
ADDZ 0.23+dt ROTX -90 ADDY 0.03 ADDX 0.40 ADDZ -0.03 cprism_ frame_mat2, frame_mat2, gs_frame_mat, 5,0.59, 0,0,15, 0.03,0,15, 0.03,0.03,15, 0,0.03,15, 0,0,-1 DEL 5
ADDZ 0.50+dt ROTX -90 ADDY 0.03 ADDX 0.63 ADDZ -0.03 cprism_ frame_mat2, frame_mat2, gs_frame_mat, 5,0.59, 0,0,15, 0.03,0,15, 0.03,0.03,15, 0,0.03,15, 0,0,-1 DEL 5
ADDZ 0.53+dt ROTY 90 ADDY -0.01 ADDX 0.03 ADDZ 0.23 cprism_ frame_mat2, frame_mat2, gs_frame_mat, 5,0.46, 0,0,15, 0.03,0,15, 0.03,0.08,15, 0,0.08,15, 0,0,-1 DEL 5
ADDZ 0.53+dt ROTY 90 ADDY 0.46 ADDX 0.03 ADDZ 0.23 cprism_ frame_mat2, frame_mat2, gs_frame_mat, 5,0.46, 0,0,15, 0.03,0,15, 0.03,0.08,15, 0,0.08,15, 0,0,-1 DEL 5
Material gs_seat_mat alfa=ATN((gs_seat_height-0.3063+0.37)/0.17) ADD 0.46, 0, 0.1 ROTY 90-alfa ADD -0.015, 0, -0.07 CUTPOLYA 5, 1, 0, 0, 0, 15, 1, 0, 15, 1, zzyzx, 15, 0, zzyzx, 15, 0, 0, -1 DEL 3
ADDZ 0.33+dt ROTY 90 ROTY 11 ADDY 0.065 ADDX 0.03 ADDZ -0.03 BRICK 0.015,0.4, 0.52+0.2 DEL 6
CUTEND
Material gs_back_mat alfa=ATN((gs_seat_height-0.3063+0.37)/0.17) ADD 0.46, 0, 0.1 ROTY 90-alfa ADD -0.015, 0.075, -0.07 BRICK 0.015, 0.38, 0.07+(zzyzx-0.1-0.015*COS(alfa))/SIN(alfa) DEL 3
ENDIF
DEL 3
DEL 1
Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2 DLEV3D_DRAFT = 3
! Designer Chair 09 EPS=0.001
If gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 If gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 If gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_DETAILED then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2
gs_OrigoCentered = 0
dim stSymbolTypes[16] stSymbolTypes[ 1] = `Круглый` stSymbolTypes[ 2] = `Круглый со Спинкой` stSymbolTypes[ 3] = `Прямоугольный` stSymbolTypes[ 4] = `Прямоугольный со Спинкой 1` stSymbolTypes[ 5] = `Трапециевидный` stSymbolTypes[ 6] = `Трапециевидный со Спинкой` stSymbolTypes[ 7] = `Криволинейный` stSymbolTypes[ 8] = `Криволинейный со Спинкой` stSymbolTypes[ 9] = `Прямоугольный со Спинкой 3` stSymbolTypes[10] = `Прямоугольный со Спинкой 2` stSymbolTypes[11] = `Круглый со Спинкой 2` stSymbolTypes[12] = `Круглый со Спинкой 3` stSymbolTypes[13] = `Криволинейный со Спинкой 2` stSymbolTypes[14] = `Криволинейный со Спинкой 3` stSymbolTypes[15] = `Детальный 1` stSymbolTypes[16] = `Детальный 2`
dt=gs_seat_height-0.3063 alfa=ATN((gs_seat_height-0.3063+0.37)/0.17)
Symbol.Script_VL:
HIDEPARAMETER ALL "A", "B", "zzyzx"
call "FM_types" parameters all
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_SIMPLE, `Простой`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.`
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF then lock "gs_shadow", "gs_full_edit" hideparameter "gs_shadow", "gs_full_edit" endif
call "2dDetailLevel" parameters gs_detlevel_2D = gs_detlevel_2D, gs_detlevel_2D_m = gs_detlevel_2D_m, returned_parameters gs_detlevel_2D_m
if gs_detlevel_2D_m <> 4 then HIDEPARAMETER "gs_SymbolType" lock "gs_SymbolType", "gs_SymbolType_m" endif
call "fa_ChairSymbol" parameters all stSymbolTypes = stSymbolTypes
IF gs_cont_pen=0 THEN parameters gs_cont_pen=4 IF gs_fill_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=19
values "gs_seat_height" range [0.21, zzyzx-0.2] values "zzyzx" range [gs_seat_height + 0.2,)
! --- Minimal Space ---
VALUES "MSFront" RANGE [0,) VALUES "MSSide" RANGE [0,) VALUES "MSRear" RANGE [0,)
Symbol.Script_UI:
UI_dialog `Параметры Стула`
ui_current_page gs_ui_current_page
dim tabTitles[4] tabTitles[1] = `Размеры и Минимальное Пространство` tabTitles[2] = `2D-отображение` tabTitles[3] = `3D-отображение и Покрытия` tabTitles[4] = `Характеристики`
dim tabIcons[4] tabIcons[1] = "uiTab_Dimension_flat(1)" tabIcons[2] = "uiTab_2DRepr_flat(1)" tabIcons[3] = "uiTab_3DRepr_flat(1)" tabIcons[4] = "uiTab_Descriptions_flat(1)"
FILE_DEPENDENCE "uiTab_Dimension_flat(1)" FILE_DEPENDENCE "uiTab_2DRepr_flat(1)" FILE_DEPENDENCE "uiTab_3DRepr_flat(1)" FILE_DEPENDENCE "uiTab_Descriptions_flat(1)"
iPageIDRoot =-1 iPageIDDimMinSpace = 1 iPageID2DRepresentation = 2 iPageID3DRepresentation = 3 iPageIDDescriptions = 4
pageStartY = 5 ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ !UI_PAGES ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
UI_PAGE iPageIDDimMinSpace, iPageIDRoot, tabTitles[1], tabIcons[1] gosub "dimMinSpacePage"
UI_PAGE iPageID2DRepresentation, iPageIDRoot, tabTitles[2], tabIcons[2] gosub "2DPage"
UI_PAGE iPageID3DRepresentation, iPageIDRoot, tabTitles[3], tabIcons[3] gosub "3DPage"
UI_PAGE iPageIDDescriptions, iPageIDRoot, tabTitles[4], tabIcons[4] gosub "descriptionPage"
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ end ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ !Subroutines ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ "dimMinSpacePage": ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
x1 = 0 x2 = 228 y0 = pageStartY + 4
ui_outfield `Высота Сидения`, x1, y0, 168, 15 ui_infield "gs_seat_height", 169, y0 - 4, 90, 19
ui_separator 0, y0 + 21, 444, y0 + 21
pageStartY = pageStartY + 29
call "ui_chairs_minimalspace" parameters MSType = 1, ! MINSPACE_SIMPCHAIR MSSide = MSSide, pageStartY = pageStartY
return
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ "2DPage": ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ call "ui_object_2DRepresentation" parameters iSymbolClass = 14, gs_SymbolType_m = gs_SymbolType_m, stSymbolTypes = stSymbolTypes, gs_detlevel_2D_m = gs_detlevel_2D_m, gs_2DSeat = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type = gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen = gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen = gs_back_pen, iFillListID = iPageID2DRepresentation
return
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ "3DPage": ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ dim surfacesArray[4] surfacesArray[1] = "gs_frame_mat" surfacesArray[2] = "frame_mat2" surfacesArray[3] = "gs_seat_mat" surfacesArray[4] = "gs_back_mat"
dim childFlagArray[4] childFlagArray[1] = 0 childFlagArray[2] = 0 childFlagArray[3] = 0 childFlagArray[4] = 0
call "ui_object_3DRepresentation" parameters bShowAnimation = 0, surfacesArray = surfacesArray, childFlagArray = childFlagArray, gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m, bShowResol = 0, gs_shadow = gs_shadow, iSurfaceListID = iPageID3DRepresentation
return
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ "descriptionPage": ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ dim stParamNames[16] stParamNames[1] = "gs_list_cost" stParamNames[2] = "gs_list_manufacturer" stParamNames[3] = "gs_list_note" stParamNames[4] = "gs_list_location" stParamNames[5] = "gs_list_accessories" stParamNames[6] = "FM_Type" stParamNames[7] = "FM_InventoryNumber" stParamNames[8] = "FM_SerialNumber" stParamNames[9] = "FM_ProductionYear" stParamNames[10] = "FM_ObjectWeight" stParamNames[11] = "FM_ObjectWeightUnit" stParamNames[12] = "gs_list_custom1" stParamNames[13] = "gs_list_custom2" stParamNames[14] = "gs_list_custom3" stParamNames[15] = "gs_list_custom4" stParamNames[16] = "gs_list_custom5"
call "ui_object_listing" parameters all listfieldID = iPageIDDescriptions, listFieldPosY = 0, listFieldHeight = 265, stDescHeader = "", stValueHeader = "", stParamNames = stParamNames return
Symbol.Comment: Дизайнерский стул с 2D-символами и минимальным пространством.
